and drive him into a corner.

567
00:36:09,041 --> 00:36:11,294
-Then, he'll crumble on his own.
-What's your plan?

568
00:36:13,045 --> 00:36:15,256
I must go into the tiger's den.

569
00:36:16,257 --> 00:36:17,175
I'll call you.

570
00:36:25,391 --> 00:36:26,517
Keep him for a few days.

571
00:36:27,185 --> 00:36:28,227
Okay.

572
00:36:31,647 --> 00:36:34,650
How did Assemblyman Lee find out
about LD Global?

573
00:36:35,067 --> 00:36:37,528
