575
00:36:43,284 --> 00:36:45,995
No, not yet. He went to Naon Accounting.

576
00:36:46,078 --> 00:36:48,080
-What?
-But he had already left by the time

577
00:36:48,164 --> 00:36:49,999
-the investigation team arrived.
-You idiot!

578
00:36:51,459 --> 00:36:53,085
-Hey, Prosecutor Seo.
-Yes, sir.

579
00:36:53,169 --> 00:36:54,378
You moron!

580
00:36:54,462 --> 00:36:56,547
-Is this the best you can do?
-I'm sorry.

581
00:36:56,631 --> 00:36:59,091
Find Jang Tae-jun
and bring him to me immediately.

582
00:36:59,175 --> 00:37:00,509
Yes, sir.

583
00:37:03,179 --> 00:37:04,013
We should go.

584
00:37:05,014 --> 00:37:06,515
Damn it. That bastard.

585
00:37:35,169 --> 00:37:38,256
I'm keeping him for the time being.

586
00:37:39,215 --> 00:37:41,217
What do you think he told me?

587
00:37:45,221 --> 00:37:46,639
What are you getting at?

588
00:37:47,431 --> 00:37:48,724
