589
00:37:50,851 --> 00:37:52,144
No, I want everyone to survive.

590
00:37:53,437 --> 00:37:54,272
Including you

591
00:37:55,564 --> 00:37:56,732
and me.

592
00:38:00,861 --> 00:38:02,738
