600
00:38:26,762 --> 00:38:27,680
Yes.

601
00:38:29,223 --> 00:38:31,475
Go ahead and charge me
for blackmailing you as well.

602
00:38:32,059 --> 00:38:33,769
You've already dumped
all your garbage on me.

603
00:38:34,353 --> 00:38:36,522
Adding that to the list
won't make much of a difference.

604
00:38:47,325 --> 00:38:48,326
Mr. Song.

605
00:38:49,452 --> 00:38:50,703
If you want to live,

606
00:38:51,787 --> 00:38:53,205
you'd better save me first.

607
00:38:54,332 --> 00:38:55,416
Do you understand?

608
00:38:58,919 --> 00:39:00,629
Good luck with the rest of your hearing.

609
00:39:14,143 --> 00:39:15,269
Let's go.

610
00:39:20,691 --> 00:39:21,692
Take him.

611
00:39:43,339 --> 00:39:45,925
I'd like to thank all the assembly members
and the nominee

612
00:39:46,008 --> 00:39:48,427
for having attended the hearing
which lasted a very long time.

613
00:39:48,511 --> 00:39:52,348
I will now dismiss the hearing
regarding Assemblyman Song's

614
00:39:52,431 --> 00:39:54,558
nomination for Minister of Justice.

615
00:39:54,642 --> 00:39:56,811
The hearing is adjourned.

616
00:39:59,605 --> 00:40:02,942
-Good work, everyone.
-Let's go.

617
00:40:03,317 --> 00:40:05,903
What's your relationship
with Youngil Group and LD Global?

618
00:40:05,986 --> 00:40:08,280
-Please explain to us, sir
-Okay, we'll explain next time.

619
00:40:08,364 --> 00:40:10,825
-Please tell us how you're related.
-We'll tell you next time.

620
00:40:10,908 --> 00:40:13,452
What kind of company is LD Global?

621
00:40:13,619 --> 00:40:15,955
From what I know,
it's an investment company.

622
00:40:16,038 --> 00:40:18,833
What does Assemblyman Song
have anything to do with LD Global?

623
00:40:18,916 --> 00:40:21,544
I think you should ask that question
to Assemblyman Song

624
00:40:21,627 --> 00:40:24,296
since he's already acquainted
with the owner of LD Global.

625
00:40:24,380 --> 00:40:26,215
Before all these suspicions
get cleared up,

626
00:40:26,298 --> 00:40:29,385
I don't think Assemblyman Song's
hearing report

627
00:40:29,468 --> 00:40:31,053
should be approved.

628
00:40:32,888 --> 00:40:35,474
And more importantly,
I request Assemblyman Song

629
00:40:35,558 --> 00:40:37,810
to tell us the truth
regarding these suspicions himself.

630
00:40:38,394 --> 00:40:40,062
The most important issue...

631
00:40:41,981 --> 00:40:44,191
I'm so exhausted
after all that I had to go through today.

632
00:40:44,275 --> 00:40:45,568
Why did you ask me to come?

633
00:40:45,651 --> 00:40:47,570
I'm not the one who asked for you.

634
00:40:48,529 --> 00:40:51,365
Chairman Sung returned to Korea today.

635
00:41:00,416 --> 00:41:02,418
It's been a long time, Chairman Sung.

636
00:41:07,214 --> 00:41:08,632
How was your trip?

637
00:41:08,716 --> 00:41:10,468
You came back earlier than planned.

638
00:41:12,428 --> 00:41:15,181
Why do you think I had to

639
00:41:15,764 --> 00:41:16,932
alter my schedule?

640
00:41:17,850 --> 00:41:20,352
I want you to step down from the candidacy

641
00:41:20,436 --> 00:41:22,730
for Minister of Justice
before things get out of hand.

642
00:41:23,772 --> 00:41:24,648
Sir.

643
00:41:24,732 --> 00:41:27,193
I don't need to hear any more from you.

644
00:41:27,276 --> 00:41:28,360
You don't need to worry.

645
00:41:28,444 --> 00:41:31,906
-I'll make sure this doesn't affect you--
-Mr. Song.

646
00:41:31,989 --> 00:41:34,617
Is it so hard for you
to understand what I'm saying?

647
00:41:36,160 --> 00:41:40,080
I hope you didn't forget who helped you

648
00:41:40,414 --> 00:41:42,166
come this far in the first place.

649
00:41:42,833 --> 00:41:44,335
Of course not, sir.

650
00:42:02,394 --> 00:42:04,647
If the hearing progress report
isn't approved,

651
00:42:04,730 --> 00:42:07,274
it'll impose a great deal
of pressure on the Blue House.

652
00:42:07,358 --> 00:42:08,984
As the former minister stepped down,

653
00:42:09,068 --> 00:42:12,947
